(670,	1,	'2022-11-21 07:28:47',	'2022-11-21 07:28:47',	'<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Shipping &amp; Delivery</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Glory offers free shipping on all domestic orders above Rs.799 of jewellery placed on our website. This policy is also applicable to all COD payments (if offered).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We at Glory believe in 100% transparency, and we want to deliver exactly what we have committed to you. We understand that getting your items quickly is important to you, so we make every effort from our end to process your order as quickly as possible. We will make the delivery on a ‘best effort’ basis after acceptance of your order. Subject to events beyond our control, the Product/s will be dispatched within 2-3 days of the acceptance of the order. After dispatch, it should get delivered at your doorstep within 6-8 business days.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We generally ship through the trusted courier companies like FirstFlight, BlueDart, FedEx etc. but we may use other services depending on factors like destination location coverage etc. In smaller cities where these carriers do not provide service, delivery may take an additional 2-3 days because of additional shipping time by other courier services.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We will communicate the dispatch details to you and will ship the Product/s to the mailing address provided by you while placing the order. If you do not receive the Product/s within a reasonable period of time, you should immediately notify us through <a href=\"mailto:glorify.urself13@gmail.com\">glorify.urself13@gmail.com</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We will also send communication once the delivery is confirmed by the courier partner. Customer shall reach out to us within 2-3 days of delivery confirmation for any delivery related issue. After this period, we may not be liable for any non-delivery claims.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In some instances it takes longer to dispatch the shipment, the same will be mentioned on the product detail page or will be communicated to the buyer; in all other cases the aforementioned free shipping policy applies. Under all other unavoidable circumstances which may cause delay, we shall update you to the contact modes provided by you.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You as a buyer have an obligation to forthwith check the product/s for damage upon receipt of the same. If the box in which the item has arrived has extensive visible damage, you are requested to put a comment behind the receipt &amp; contact us within 24 hrs. If the product/s are damaged, then please don’t sign the receipt &amp; contact us immediately. Our liability for damaged goods ceases once you sign the delivery receipt without any comments.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Cancellation &amp; Refunds</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We reserve the right to cancel an order in case the order request is not acceptable to us. Upon such cancellation, we will give you a full refund. Any such cancellation shall be at the sole discretion of Glory and you will have no right to contest the same. The reasons for cancellation could be due to non-availability of the Product/s, inaccuracy in Product or pricing information or due to reasons of any fraud or wrong usage of payment mechanism adopted by you. Any cancellation will be intimated to you by us over phone or mail.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In the event you desire to cancel any order, then, such cancellation must be done prior to the dispatch of the Product/s to you. Once dispatched, we will not accept any cancellation request from your end. Please call us or email us at <a href=\"mailto:glorify.urself13@gmail.com\">glorify.urself13@gmail.com</a> to notify us about the cancellation.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you cancel part of the order, where shipping charges are applicable then it will not be refunded.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If the order is cancelled by us, lost or un-delivered to your preferred location, we will provide you a full refund including shipping charges.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In all monetary refunds, we reserve the right to choose the mode of refund. The refund payment will be made by way of online transfer as per our preference within 7 days after confirmation from us. Confirmation is subject to quality confirmation and acceptance by us as per policy. The money amount refunded will be what is paid to us after discounts/ promotions.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For any further queries regarding cancellation/refunds, please email us at : <a href=\"mailto:glorify.urself13@gmail.com\">glorify.urself13@gmail.com</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Returns &amp; Replacements</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Glory offers you a 5-day Return on all products that you purchase from us. To qualify for full refund against return, the below criteria should be met:<br>a. We offer a free replacement/refund only for product/s which is/ are damaged /broken or significantly different from website description.<br>b. Meeting Shipping &amp; Delivery policy is must for Returns &amp; Replacement eligibility.<br>c. In case of significantly different, the product/s must be in an absolutely unworn and brand new condition and must be returned with the original sealed box, invoice, tags, instruction papers, warranty and other accessories if any. Make sure you have not used the product. Scratched and Used Products will not be taken back.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you return any order delivered to you, original shipping charges (if any) will not be refunded. However, if you self-ship your returns, you will be reimbursed according to the shipping amount on the shipping slip provided to us (max. up to INR 100).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>All loss or damage while returning from you is your responsibility. We will not be liable for any such incidents. For all self-shipped returns, we recommend you use a reliable courier service.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>When we receive the returned item, it will be inspected to ensure everything is present and in its original condition and then issue either a full refund (bound per refund policy) or a different item in exchange (bound per exchange policy), as per your request.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Exchange</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Glory offers you a 7-day Exchange of jewelry with any other item available on our website if you meet the criteria mentioned below:<br>a. All Exchanges are welcome within the 7 days period from the day of receipt of product/s, regardless of any reasons or questions asked.<br>b. The product/s must be in an absolutely unworn and brand-new condition and must be returned with the original sealed box, invoice, tags, instruction papers, warranty and other accessories if any.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>All loss or damage while returning from you is your responsibility. We will not be liable for any such incidents. For all self-shipped returns, we recommend you use a reliable courier service.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In case of exchange, the customer will have to pay the difference between the new product chosen and the valuation of the old product before dispatch.<br>We will contact you as soon as possible or for any further queries please email us at : glorify.urself13@gmail.com</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -